%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20a%20divorced%20mom%2C%20the%20holidays%20can%20be%20hard.%20I%20take%20care%20of%20myself%20when%20my%20kids%20are%20with%20my%20ex.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20looking%20at%20Christmas%20tree%20while%20sitting%20on%20sofa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6745d425ede4eeae392990a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20shares%20custody%20of%20her%20children%20during%20the%20holiday%3Cp%3ECavan%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%2FCavan%20Images%20RF%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20a%20mom%20of%20two%20and%20share%20custody%20with%20my%20ex-husband.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20prepare%20gifts%20early%20and%20focus%20on%20self-care%20when%20they%20are%20not%20with%20me.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20they%20get%20older%2C%20they%20still%20want%20to%20do%20holiday%20things%20with%20me%2C%20which%20makes%20me%20happy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20the%20last%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-estranged-from-parents-holidays-hard-until-she-had-kid-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristmas%20as%20a%20family%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20was%20the%20star%20on%20the%20tree%2C%20presents%20wrapped%20for%20the%20kids%2C%20and%20eggnog%20in%20the%20fridge%2C%20all%20while%20I%20was%20fending%20fights%20with%20my%20now%20ex-husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20signed%20a%20lease%20on%20an%20apartment%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20later%2C%20I%20left%20behind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fwhere-to-buy-real-christmas-trees-online%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Christmas%20tree%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20stockings%2C%20the%20nutcrackers%2C%20and%20every%20ornament.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20a%20new%20tree%20and%20ordered%20Christmas%20stockings%2C%20new%20ornaments%2C%20and