%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20Senate%20report%20warns%20of%20economic%20risks%20as%20climate%20change%20destabilizes%20insurance%20markets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHomeowners%20across%20the%20country%20are%20increasingly%20facing%20a%20stark%20new%20reality%3A%20they're%20losing%20their%20home%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20share%20of%20home%20insurance%20policies%20from%20large%20insurers%20that%20weren't%20renewed%20increased%20last%20year%20in%2046%20states%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2Fnext_to_fall_the_climate-driven_insurance_crisis_is_here__and_getting_worse.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20Wednesday%20by%20the%20Senate%20Budget%20Committee%20found.%20The%20increasing%20frequency%20and%20intensity%20of%20disasters%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsurance-losses-climate-change-hurricanes-flooding-extreme-weather-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildfires%2C%20hurricanes%2C%20and%20flooding%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-shortage-prices-construction-industry-obstacles-nimby-worker-shortage-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erising%20cost%20of%20rebuilding%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20pushed%20many%20insurers%20to%20drop%20customers%20or%20hike%20premiums.%20This%20has%20left%20thousands%20of%20homeowners%20scrambling%20to%20find%20new%20insurance%20policies%20or%20joining%20the%20growing%20ranks%20of%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2024%2F05%2F27%2Fhome-insurance-dropped-coverage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoing%20without%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20200%20counties%20saw%20their%20non-renewal%20rates%20spike%20threefold%20between%202018%20and%202023.%20Counties%20in%20Northern%20California%20and%20South%20Florida%20saw%20among%20the%20highest%20rates%20of%20nonrenewals.%20Coastal%20counties%20in%20Massachusetts%2C%20Mississippi%2C%20and%20North%20Carolina%20also%20saw%20dropped%20policies%20soar.%20Manhattan%20ranks%2020th%2C%20with%20rates%20of%20dropped%20policies%20rising%20from%201.25%25%20in%202018%20to%204.11%25%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FjLlWY%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Counties%20with%20the%20highest%20rate%20of%20home%20insurers%20dropping%20customers%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22887%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20scale%20of%20home%20insurance%20nonrenewals%20was%20previously%20unknown%20because%20insurance%20companies%20are%20regulated%20at%20the%20state%20level.%20The%20National%20Association%20of%20Insurance%20Commissioners%20said%20not%20all%20states%20collect%20granular%20data%20about%20the%20availability%20and%20affordability%20of%20coverage%20in%20some%20areas.%C2%A0The%20association%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcontent.naic.org%2Farticle%2Fstates-issue-property-casualty-market-intelligence-data-call-covering-over-80-us-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20March%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20effort%20with%20state%20insurance%20regulators%20to%20try%20to%20fill%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenate%20Budget%20Committee%20Chairman%20Sheldon%20Whitehouse%20launched%20his%20own%20investigation%20into%20the%20homeowners'%20insurance%20market%20last%20year.%20He%20received%20nonrenewal%20data%20from%2023%20companies%C2%A0accounting%20for%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20market.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2Fsenwhopening1218.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etestimony%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%2C%C2%A0Whitehouse%C2%A0said%20he%20demanded%20nonrenewal%20data%20because%20experts%20suggested%20policies%20being%20dropped%20were%20an%20early%20warning%20sign%20of%20market%20destabilization.%20He%20also%20said%20they%20correlated%20with%20higher%20premiums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Property%20Casualty%20Insurance%20Association%2C%20a%20lobbying%20group%20representing%20insurance%20companies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apci.org%2Fmedia%2Fnews-releases%2Frelease%2F83218%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20nonrenewal%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20provide%20%26quot%3Brelevant%20information%26quot%3B%20on%20climate%20risks.%20Many%20factors%2C%20including%20a%20state's%20litigation%20and%20regulatory%20environment%2C%20factor%20into%20nonrenewal%20decisions%2C%20the%20association%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20added%20that%20more%20costly%20weather%20disasters%2C%20combined%20with%20inflation%20and%20overbuilding%20in%20climate-risk%20regions%2C%20are%20making%20insurance%20less%20affordable%20for%20many%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20insurance%20premiums%20are%20rising%20in%20many%20regions%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Research%20recently%20reported%20that%20average%20home%20insurance%20premiums%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nber.org%2Fdigest%2F202410%2Fdisaster-risk-and-rising-home-insurance-premiums%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espiked%20by%2013%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%2C%20between%202020%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20mortgage%20lenders%20require%20homeowners%20to%20purchase%20insurance%2C%20and%20some%20require%20additional%20insurance%20for%20specific%20disasters%2C%20including%20flooding.%20Insurers%20refusing%20to%20offer%20coverage%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2Fwhat-homeowners-need-to-know-as-insurers-leave-high-risk-climate-areas.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehurt%20home%20values%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20homes%20that%20can't%20be%20insured%20in%20the%20private%20market%20are%20less%20desirable%20to%20potential%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Senate%20Budget%20report%20warned%20that%20the%20insurance%20crisis%20will%20get%20worse%20as%20the%20climate%20crisis%20fuels%20more%20frequent%20and%20destructive%20disasters%2C%20including%20hurricanes%2C%20wildfires%2C%20and%20flooding.%20A%20destabilized%20insurance%20market%20could%20%26quot%3Btrigger%20cascading%20economy-wide%20financial%20upheaval%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20failure%20to%20deal%20with%20climate%20change%20isn't%20just%20driving%20up%20the%20cost%20of%20homeowners'%20insurance%2C%20it's%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20families%20to%20even%20find%20homeowners'%20insurance%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20get%20a%20mortgage%2C%26quot%3B%20Whitehouse%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20pool%20of%20buyers%20is%20limited%20to%20only%20those%20who%20can%20pay%20cash%2C%20it%20cuts%20off%20pathways%20to%20homeownership%E2%80%94particularly%20for%20first-time%20homebuyers%E2%80%94and%20risks%20cascading%20into%20a%20crash%20in%20property%20values%20that%20trashes%20the%20entire%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20been%20dropped%20by%20your%20home%20insurance%20company%20or%20are%20you%20facing%20a%20steep%20premium%20increase%3F%20Email%20these%20reporters%20to%20share%20your%20story%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aerelman%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eerelman%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acboudreau%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ecboudreau%40insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F20-counties-where-home-insurers-dropping-most-customers-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%2