to%20new%20universities%20in%20a%20deal%20led%20by%20Slow%20Ventures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20were%20freshmen%20at%20Yale%2C%20Aarya%20Agarwal%20and%20his%20roommate%2C%20Samvel%20Antonyan%2C%20struck%20a%20handshake%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20either%20of%20them%20ever%20started%20a%20company%20that%20went%20supernova%2C%20they%20would%20sign%20away%2010%25%20of%20their%20income%20to%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20shook%20hands%2C%20and%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20joke%2C%26quot%3B%20Agarwal%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20realized%20the%20deal%20actually%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20economic%20sense.%20It%20was%20a%20way%20to%20multiply%20by%20two%20times%20our%20chances%20of%20doing%20something%20super%20improbable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20their%20startup%2C%20Prospinity%2C%20allows%20college%20students%20to%20enter%20into%20similar%20contracts.%20Through%20its%20platform%2C%20smart%20young%20people%20can%20join%20%26quot%3Bsuccess%20pools%26quot%3B%20of%20other%20smart%20young%20people%20who%20put%20a%20few%20percentage%20points%20of%20their%20annual%20income%20into%20a%20shared%20pot.%20Each%20year%2C%20the%20pot%20gets%20distributed%20evenly%20among%20the%20group.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%20if%20one%20of%20them%20becomes%20the%20next%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20or%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20they%20will%20all%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20year%20old%2C%20Prospinity%20is%20already%20used%20by%20students%20at%20Yale%2C%20MIT%2C%20Princeton%2C%20and%20Harvard%2C%20with%20job%20offers%20at%20firms%20like%20Blackstone%2C%20Bridgewater%2C%20and%20Amazon.%20Now%2C%20Prospinity%20has%20raised%20%242%20million%20in%20a%20round%20led%20by%20Slow%20Ventures%20managing%20director%20Kevin%20Colleran%20to%20reach%20more%20students%20beyond%20the%20Ivy%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProspinity%20and%20Slow%20Ventures%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20valuation.%20Patrick%20Chung%2C%20a%20managing%20partner%20at%20Xfund%20and%20an%20investor%20in%20Sam%20Altman's%20first%20company%2C%20Loopt%2C%20also%20joined%20the%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlow%20Ventures%20has%20explored%20income%20sharing%20as%20an%20investment%20strategy%20before.%20It%20set%20aside%20%2420%20million%20from%20recent%20funds%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fslow-ventures-set-aside-20-million-invest-in-influencers-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20equity%20in%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20taking%20a%20percentage%20of%20their%20future%20profits%20for%20a%20set%20amount%20of%20time%20in%20exchange%20for%20upfront%20capital.%20Regulatory%20filings%20show%20Slow%20is%20now%20raising%20%24275%20million%20across%20two%20new%20funds%2C%20which%20Fortune%20first%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222cd949b4-0140-4ac3-acc4-8c3c1a6fa3ce%5C%22%3EHow%20Prospinity%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prospinity%20rolls%20out%20to%20a%20new%20university%2C%20it%20researches%20the%20student%20body%20and%20selects%20a%20handful%20of%20high%20achievers%20to%20create%20or%20join%20a%20success%20pool.%20They%20can%20hop%20onto%20Prospinity%2C%20check%20out%20the%20profiles%20of%20existing%20members%2C%20and%20filter%20by%20university%20or%20industry.%20Prospinity%20is%20now%20recruiting%20students%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20to%20join%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProspinity%20says%20the%20contracts%20are%20legally%20binding%20and%20can%20ensure%20everyone%20pays%20their%20fair%20share%20over%20the%20agreement's%20term%2C%20typically%2010%20years.%20Pool%20members%20can%20also%20set%20a%20minimum%20income%3B%20if%20someone's%20earnings%20fall%20below%20the%20threshold%2C%20they're%20excluded%20from%20that%20year's%20distribution.%20Prospinity%20takes%20a%205%25%20distribution%20cut%20in%20exchange%20for%20providing%20the%20technical%20and%20legal%20infrastructure%20to%20execute%20the%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20company's%20hundreds%20of%20members%20are%20mostly%20still%20in%20school%2C%20they%20can%20start%20collecting%20distributions%20as%20other%20pool%20members%20contribute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgarwal%2C%20who%20studied%20computer%20science%20and%20economics%20at%20Yale%20before%20he%20dropped%20out%20to%20focus%20on%20Prospinity%2C%20said%20the%20company's%20premise%20is%20loosely%20based%20on%20the%20power%20law%2C%20a%20principle%20in%20venture%20capital%20that%20describes%20how%20a%20small%20number%20of%20investments%20often%20create%20the%20majority%20of%20returns%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20either%20break%20even%20or%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20markets%20get%20more%20efficient%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20more%20and%20more%20of%20these%20distributions%20where%20a%20few%20people%20make%20it%20big%2C%20and%20then%20everyone%20else%20tends%20to%20be%20left%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20Agarwal%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20success%20pools%20are%20going%20to%20be%20a%20very%20important%20way%20to%20hedge%20against%20that%20sort%20of%20uncertainty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20founders%2C%20Agarwal%20and%20Antonyan%20along%20with%20Andrea%20Zanon%20and%20Andrea%20De%20Berardinis%2C%20belong%20to%20a%20larger%20success%20pool%20that%20agreed%20to%20share%202%25%20of%20their%20income%20over%20a%2010-year%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224fb3e876-1aa4-4af7-8f51-dc848246f6cd%5C%22%3EProspinity%20rolls%20out%20to%20more%20students%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHassaan%20Qadir%2C%20a%20Yale%20senior%20who%20took%20a%20semester%20off%20to%20start%20a%20company%20developing%20software%20for%20biology%20researchers%2C%20joined%20a%20Prospinity%20pool.%20He%20later%20folded%20the%20startup%20and%20accepted%20an%20internship%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapplovin-meteoric-rise-some-advertisers-have-big-questions-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAppLovin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Palo%20Alto%20company%20that%20provides%20marketing%20services%20to%20mobile%20app%20developers.%20Qadir%20plans%20to%20start%20another%20tech%20company%20someday%20and%20said%20being%20part%20of%20an%20income-sharing%20agreement%20with%20other%20founders%20gives%20him%20more%20chances%20of%20hitting%20the%20entrepreneurial%20jackpot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaw%20school%20students%2C%20finance%20associates%2C%20and%20aspiring%20entrepreneurs%20compose%20his%20success%20pool%20of%20about%2030%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheoretically%2C%20someone%20that%20you%20know%20is%20going%20to%20become%20really%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Qadir%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20totally%20up%20to%20who%20works%20the%20hardest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAron%20Ravin%2C%20another%20member%20of%20that%20same%20Prospinity%20pool%2C%20hopes%20to%20capture%20some%20potential%20upsides%20of%20being%20an%20entrepreneur%20as%20he%20climbs%20the%20corporate%20ladder.%20He%20joined%20that%20Prospinity%20pod%20during%20his%20senior%20year%20at%20Yale%20and%20now%20works%20as%20an%20associate%20at%20a%20prominent%20hedge%20fund.%20Ravin%20stands%20to%20make%20good%20money%20in%20finance%2C%20although%20he%20said%20he%20may%20not%20hit%20the%20jackpot%20as%20someone%20starting%20the%20next%20Uber%20or%20Palantir%20might.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavin%20declined%20to%20share%20how%20much%20of%20his%20income%20he's%20contributing%20to%20the%20pool%20but%20said%20it's%20between%201%25%20and%205%25.%20At%20a%20Prospinity%20mixer%20in%20New%20Haven%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20he%20mingled%20with%20some%20international%20students%20working%20on%20a%20sustainability%20venture%2C%20which%20got%20him%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20little%20promiscuous%20of%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ravin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20maybe%20I'll%20join%20another%20pool%20in%20the%20future.%20Share%20the%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprospinity-income-sharing-