d%20to%20turn%20the%20business%20into%20a%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20business%2C%20Collectable%20Cities%2C%20makes%20art%20toys%20for%20the%20high-end%20souvenir%20market%2C%20but%20the%20pair%20had%20reached%20the%20%26quot%3Bsoul-destroying%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20the%20business%20where%20practical%20issues%20turned%20the%20spark%20into%20a%20slog%2C%20Derer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20you%20see%20someone%20else%20make%20a%20video%2C%20where%20you%20can%20feel%20their%20pain%20through%20the%20screen%20and%20it's%20like%2C%20'I%20should%20be%20also%20sharing%20some%20of%20this%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20to%20their%20video%20spanned%20thousands%20of%20comments%2C%20giving%20them%20exposure%20to%20new%20customers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20wealth%20of%20feedback%20and%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlice%20Bull%2C%20founder%20of%20Gratified%2C%20a%20TikTok-focused%20strategy%20and%20content%20agency%2C%20says%20she%20finds%20these%20kinds%20of%20posts%20compelling%20and%20has%20even%20ordered%20from%20businesses%20after%20seeing%20them.%20She%20characterizes%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bstorytelling%20hook%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20five%20tried-and-tested%20approaches%20that%20she%20says%20tend%20to%20produce%20results%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBull%20regularly%20encourages%20her%20clients%20to%20not%20just%20showcase%20their%20products%2C%20but%20to%20pull%20back%20the%20curtain%20on%20their%20own%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTelling%20stories%2C%20especially%20on%20TikTok%20right%20now%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20things%20you%20can%20do%2C%20particularly%20with%20a%20small%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20you%20can%20do%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20audience%20that%20will%20potentially%20become%20your%20customers%20is%20absolutely%20vital%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20one%20of%20the%20quickest%20ways%20you%20can%20do%20that%20is%20by%20being%20slightly%20dramatic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20research%20shows%20that%20emotionally%20positive%20content%20gets%20the%20best%20engagement%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-creators-rage-farm-on-tiktok-and-why-its-on-the-rise-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enegative%20content%20has%20its%20own%20pull%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jmis.org%2Farchive%2Fview_article_pubreader%3Fpid%3Djmis-10-2-153%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%202023%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20tracked%20the%20eye%20movement%20of%20TikTok%20and%20Twitter%20users%20suggested%20that%20viewers%20spend%20more%20time%20on%20negative%20rather%20than%20positive%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20works%20because%20people%20immediately%20want%20to%20know%20what%20happened%2C%20Bull%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20either%20experience%20that%20emotion%20with%20that%20person%20or%20understand%20what%20they%20went%20through%26quot%3B%20in%20order%20to%20save%20yourself%20from%20the%20same%20fate%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20also%20be%20a%20smart%20way%20of%20adding%20context%20to%20unpopular%20decisions%20like%20price%20hikes%2C%20Bull%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237c2ea5c-3ab3-40b2-843b-48ca115b6f75%5C%22%3EStaying%20authentic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDone%20right%2C%20the%20hook%20can%20tap%20into%20the%20authenticism%20that%20has%20underpinned%20other%20TikTok%20trends%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeinfluencing-is-the-anti-influencer-trend-rich-with-paradoxes-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeinfluencing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fdiscover%2Fsocial-media-isnt-real%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20media%20isn't%20real%26quot%3B%20hook%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20an%20obvious%20business%20risk%20to%20telling%20the%20world%20you're%20failing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20adopt%20this%20strategy%20need%20to%20weigh%20up%20the%20risk%20of%20harm%20to%20their%20long-term%20reputation%20with%20the%20benefits%20of%20appealing%20to%20people%20through%20honesty%2C%20Bull%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20potential%20ethical%20problem%20that%20comes%20with%20virality%20%E2%80%94%20if%20declaring%20your%20troubles%20is%20such%20an%20effective%20cash%20lever%2C%20there'll%20always%20be%20the%20temptation%20for%20successful%20businesses%20to%20exaggerate%20or%20even%20lie%20about%20their%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20so%20many%20iterations%20have%20proliferated%20on%20the%20platform%20that%20it's%20been%20boiled%20down%20to%20something%20like%20a%20script%2C%20with%20audio%20from%20particularly%20successful%20versions%20borrowed%20by%20others%2C%20who%20simply%20paste%20it%20over%20their%20own%20visuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERivero%20said%20that%20quality%20also%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20just%20going%20to%20buy%20a%20product%20just%20because%20I%20like%20the%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20needs%20to%20come%20hand-in-hand%20with%20a%20good%20quality%20product.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20a%20dropshipper%20who%20makes%20the%20same%20complaint%20as%20a%20one-person%20craft%20business%20is%20unlikely%20to%20get%20much%20sympathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22185d30da-cf3e-4f23-a42a-bb3e766599a8%5C%22%3EBuilding%20trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELaura%20Craine%20said%20that%20the%20massive%20response%20to%20her%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20business%20is%20failing%26quot%3B%20post%20was%20part%20of%20what%20rallied%20her%20to%20carry%20on%20with%20her%20craft%20business%20when%20she%20was%20almost%20ready%20to%20close%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%2C%20my%20videos%20weren't%20doing%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20But%20this%20one%20took%20off%2C%20bringing%20her%20hundreds%20of%20new%20followers%20and%20a%20wealth%20of%20supportive%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECraine's%20business%2C%20With%20Love%20And%20Dreams%2C%20preserves%20personal%20items%20like%20wedding%20blooms%20or%20human%20remains%20in%20resin%20to%20create%20memorial%20keepsakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20she%20handles%20sensitive%20and%20irreplaceable%20items%20means%20her%20business%20depends%20on%20maintaining%20a%20deep%20wellspring%20of%20trust.%20Being%20completely%20authentic%20with%20her%20audience%20just%20made%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20people%20to%20see%20that%20I'm%20a%20real%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-unexpected-tiktok-hook-thats-saving-small-businesses-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734947488000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6760065527808b3289cd4cc0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-unexpected-tiktok-hook-thats-saving-small-businesses-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%20small%20business%20is%20failing%26quot%3B%20has%20become%20a%20surprisingly%20useful%20post%20for%20entrepreneurs%20on%20TikTok.%20Here's%20how%20and%20why%20it%20works%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20the%20pitfalls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mjankowicz%40businessinsider.com%20(Mia%20Jankowicz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-unexpected-tiktok-hook-thats-saving-small-businesses-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIntention%20To%20Dupe%20UPSC%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-IAS%20Trainee%20Puja%20Khedkar%20Denied%20Pre-Arrest%20Bail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fdelhi-high-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20High%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20denied%20anticipatory%20bail%20to%20former%20IAS%20trainee%20officer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fpuja-khedkar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuja%20Khedkar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20made%20headlines%20in%20June%20and%20August%20amid%20claims%20she%20lied%20about%20physical%20and%20mental%20disabilities%2C%20and%20changed%20her%20name%20and%20surname%2C%20as%20well%20as%20forging%20an%20OBC%20certificate%2C%20to%20clear%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20her%20intensions%2C%20prima%20facie%2C%20were%20to%20dupe%20authorities%20and%20observed%20%26quot%3Bher%20steps%20(were)%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20conspiracy.%20Ms%20Khedkar%2C%20it%20was%20also%20observed%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bunfit%20for%20appointment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charges%20against%20her%2C%20which%20include%20forgery%20and%20cheating%2C%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bclassic%20example%20of%20fraud%20committed%20not%20only%20an%20authority%20but%20also%20the%20nation%20at%20large%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20said%20Monday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConduct%20of%20the%20petitioner%20was%20purely%20driven%20with%20a%20motive%20to%20dupe%20the%20complainant%20UPSC%2C%20or%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%2C%20and%20all%20documents%20allegedly%20forged%20by%20her%20were%20done%20to%20reap%20benefits%20of%20schemes%20meant%20for%20the%20(disadvantaged)%20groups%20of%20the%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investigation%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20as%20per%20material%20available%20on%20the%20record%2C%20prima%20facie%20reveals%20the%20petitioner%20is%20not%20a%20fit%20candidate%20to%20avail%20benefits%20meant%20for%20disadvantaged%20groups...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20mention%2C%20the%20court%20also%20indicated%20%26quot%3Ba%20high%20possibility%20that%20family%20members%20(of%20Ms%20Khedkar)%20may%20have%20coll