20cut%205%2C500%20positions%2C%20many%20of%20which%20were%20managers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20budget%20process%20can%20be%20a%20parade%20of%20lengthy%20meetings%20and%20red%20tape%20%E2%80%94%20so%20one%20CEO%20decided%20to%20try%20something%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20becoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbayer-bill-anderson-ceo-corporate-hierarchy-get-rid-of-bosses-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20at%20Bayer%2C%20Bill%20Anderson%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20introduced%20a%20set%20of%20striking%20changes%20to%20the%20company%2C%20including%20an%20overhaul%20of%20its%20budget%20system%2C%20which%20he%20sees%20as%20the%20driving%20source%20of%20corporate%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20know%20that%20the%20belly%20of%20the%20beast%20of%20bureaucracy%20is%20the%20budget%20process%2C%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20knows%20that.%20Everyone%20hates%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%2090%20days%2C%20Anderson%20reallocates%20budgets%20for%20the%20next%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20take%20the%20company%20%26quot%3B90%20days%20at%20a%20time%26quot%3B%20was%20inspired%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bradical%20experiment%26quot%3B%20he%20helped%20implement%20at%20Genentech%20in%202016%20before%20becoming%20CEO%20of%20the%20biotech%20company%20in%202017.%20After%20what%20he%20described%20as%20an%20unsuccessful%20attempt%20to%20de-bureaucratize%20the%20budgeting%20process%20at%20Genentech%2C%20Anderson%20said%20Genentech%20decided%20to%20%26quot%3Bkill%20all%20budgets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20plan%20didn't%20lead%20to%20lower%20spending%2C%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20company%20spending%20at%20Genentech%20went%20down%20in%20the%20first%20year%2C%20it%20shot%20right%20back%20up%20a%20year%20later%2C%20Anderson%20said.%20While%20the%20CEO%20didn't%20want%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20old%20process%2C%20he%20concluded%20he%20had%20to%20find%20something%20to%20replace%20it%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenentech%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20brought%20the%20lesson%20to%20German%20life%20science%20company%20Bayer%2C%20where%2C%20a%20month%20after%20becoming%20CEO%20in%20June%202023%2C%20he%20replaced%20annual%20budget%20discussions%20with%2090-day%20cycles.%20Instead%20of%20managers%20spending%20five%20months%20setting%20targets%20and%20forecasting%2C%20Anderson%20said%20squads%20come%20together%20every%2090%20days%20to%20discuss%20whether%20the%20company%20achieved%20its%20goals%2C%20how%20it%20used%20resources%2C%20and%20what%20it%20needs%20to%20focus%20on%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conventional%20budget%20process%2C%20Anderson%20said%20the%20team%20would%20be%20discussing%20what%20they're%20going%20to%20do%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20a%20year%20ahead.%20The%20problem%20with%20that%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20knows%26quot%3B%20what%20they'll%20be%20doing%20that%20far%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20waste%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20negotiating%20over%20budgets%20for%20Q4%20next%20year.%20They%20don't%20even%20know%20what%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20budget%20overhaul%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20restructuring%20which%20the%20company%20refers%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BDynamic%20Shared%20Ownership.%26quot%3B%20In%20addition%20to%20flipping%20the%20budget%20system%2C%20the%20model%20also%20reorganizes%20staff%20every%2090%20days%20into%20%26quot%3Bmini%20networks%26quot%3B%20made%20up%20of%20who%20is%20best%20suited%20to%20lead%20that%20specific%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20every%2090%20days%2C%20people%20can%20flow%20between%20teams%2C%20money%20can%20flow%20between%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you're%20working%20on%20the%20most%20important%20things%20for%20the%20next%2090%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bayer.com%2Fmedia%2Fen-us%2Fbayer-aims-to-sustainably-improve-performance-with-new-organization%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannouncing%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20new%20operating%20model%20in%20January%202024%2C%20the%20company%20said%20the%20structure%20would%20%26quot%3Breduce%20hierarchies%2C%20eliminate%20bureaucracy%2C%20streamline%20structures%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20speed%20up%20the%20decision-making%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20select%20groups%20called%20%26quot%3Bfrontrunner%20teams%26quot%3B%20transitioned%20to%20the%20new%20model%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202023.%20Now%2C%20most%20of%20the%20company%20has%20moved%20to%20the%20new%20structure.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20managerial%20positions%20have%20changed%2C%20with%20some%20transitioning%20to%20individual%20contributors%20and%20others%20being%20laid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year%2C%20the%20company%20has%20cut%20about%205%2C500%20roles%2C%20most%20of%20which%20were%20managers%2C%20shrinking%20its%20overall%20headcount%20from%20around%20100%2C000%20down%20to%20around%2094%2C500.%20A%20spokesperson%20said%20layoffs%20are%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20said%20some%20teams%2C%20like%20those%20that%20started%20the%20transition%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20%26quot%3Bare%20racing%20ahead%20and%20doing%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20other%20groups%20are%20%26quot%3Bstill%20stuck%20in%20the%20starting%20blocks.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20the%20company's%20voluntary%20attrition%20rate%20has%20gone%20down%20since%20transitioning%20to%20the%20new%20operating%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20plan%20to%20cut%20costs%20by%20about%202%20billion%20euros%20by%202026.%20Bayer's%20stock%20price%20is%20down%2046%25%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year.%20In%20its%20third-quarter%20earnings%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bayer.com%2Fmedia%2Fen-us%2F2024-bayer-q3-media-update-speech%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20%244%20billion%20in%20net%20losses%20and%20shared%20expectations%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmuted%20outlook%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdeclining%20earnings%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20faced%20several%20recent%20headwinds%2C%20including%20the%20expected%20loss%20of%20exclusivity%20on%20the%20blood-thinning%20drug%20Xarelto.%20Anderson%20said%20the%20drug%20was%20once%20responsible%20for%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20Bayer's%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20also%20grappled%20with%20legal%20battles%20over%20Roundup%2C%20a%20herbicide%20produced%20by%20Monsanto%2C%20which%20Bayer%20purchased%20for%20%2463%20billion%20in%202018.%20The%20product%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20thousands%20of%20lawsuits%20alleging%20it%20causes%20cancer%2C%20and%20Bayer%20agreed%20to%20pay%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20resolve%20some%20of%20the%20litigation%20while%20it%20also%20appeals%20some%20of%20the%20court%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edecisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20litigation%20topic%20is%20a%20big%20overhang%20for%20our%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20things%20happening%26quot%3B%20but%20investors%20want%20the%20company%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20lawsuits%2C%20which%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Bayer%20announced%20the%20new%20operating%20model%2C%20the%20company%20said%20its%20goal%20was%20to%20become%20%26quot%3Bmore%20agile%20and%20significantly%20improve%20its%20operational%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Anderson%20has%20already%20reported%20some%20positive%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Bayer's%20third-quarter%20earnings%20report%2C%20Anderson%20said%20Bayer's%20Pharma%20division%20outside%20Milan%20cut%20release%20time%20by%20almost%2050%25%2C%20resulting%20in%20less%20waste%2C%20improved%20cash%20flow%2C%20and%20lower%20inventory.%20Anderson%20said%20in%20the%20report%20that%20when%20he%20first%20asked%20about%20success%20stories%2C%20he%20would%20get%20the%20same%20two%20or%20three%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20I'm%20hearing%20stories%20like%20these%20basically%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20told%20investors.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20confident%20that%20will%20translate%20into%20results%20for%20our%20investors%2C%20and%20a%20bright%20future%20for%20us%20and%20our%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbayer-ceo-bill-anderson-annual-budget-process-alternative-90-days-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734946981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761e6091d90e3bcf31d70b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbayer-ceo-bill-anderson-annual-budget-process-alternative-90-days-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bayer%20CEO%20Bill%20Anderson%20says%20%26quot%3Beveryone%20hates%26quot%3B%20the%20budget%20process%20and%20the%20bureaucracy%20involved.%20So%20he%20implemented%2090-day%20budget%20cycles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbayer-ceo-bill-anderson-annual-budget-process-alternative-90-days-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Yeh%20Jawaani%20Hai%20Deewani%20getting%20a%20sequel%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734946896000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116596683%2Cimgsize-979741.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fre