ureaucrat%2C%20politician%2C%20or%20celeb%20to%20get%20things%20done%20easily%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh%20taxes%20without%20corresponding%20government%20services%20were%20another%20major%20grievance.%20He%20recounted%20an%20incident%20in%20Goa%20where%20he%20urged%20a%20group%20of%20people%20to%20use%20a%20bin%20instead%20of%20littering%2C%20only%20to%20be%20told%20to%20%26quot%3Bmind%20%5Bhis%5D%20own%20business%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BCivic%20sense%20has%20gone%20extinct%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20such%20encounters%20were%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%20also%20painted%20a%20grim%20picture%20of%20India's%20economy%2C%20warning%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20economic%20collapse%26quot%3B%20and%20highlighting%20the%20depreciating%20rupee.%20He%20suggested%20innovators%20consider%20relocating%20to%20countries%20such%20as%20the%20UAE%20or%20Thailand%2C%20where%20he%20believed%20the%20environment%20was%20more%20conducive%20to%20building%20something%20groundbreaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20nutshell%E2%80%A6%20leave%20the%20country%20where%20they'll%20even%20tax%20your%20popcorn%20because%20they're%20out%20of%20ideas%20to%20make%20it%20a%20%245%20trillion%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20new%20GST%20rules%20that%20impose%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgst-council-clarifies-on-popcorn-taxation-7301384%C2%A0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E18%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20popcorn%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20post%20was%20later%20removed%20by%20Reddit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734945300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F6e5aufoo_flight-generic_625x300_20_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fleave-india-entrepreneur-criticises-innovation-barriers-popcorn-taxes-7311906%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indi