%20a%20few%20simple%20and%20inexpensive%20joys%20in%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20feels%20lonely%2C%20she%20counts%20them%3A%20a%20hot-fudge%20sundae%20at%20McDonald's%20(%243.79)%2C%20a%20walk%20with%20her%20dogs%20(free)%2C%20and%20the%20first%20puff%20of%20her%20cigarette%20(%249.63%20for%20a%20pack)%20on%20a%20sunny%20afternoon%20in%20northern%20California.%20The%2068-year-old%20repeats%20the%20list%20over%20and%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20those%20moments%20where%20I'm%20wishing%20I%20had%20a%20friend%20that%20I%20could%20do%20something%20with%2C%20I%20just%20gravitate%20toward%20my%20dogs%20and%20say%2C%20oh%2C%20I%20got%20two%20friends%20right%20here%20%E2%80%94%20let's%20go%20for%20a%20walk%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20mid-September%2C%20more%20than%203%2C300%20older%20Americans%20like%20Ozenne%20have%20shared%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-americans-regret-retirement-savings-taking-social-security-early-investments-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%20regrets%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Business%20Insider%20through%20a%20reader%20survey%20or%20direct%20emails%20to%20reporters.%20Loneliness%20is%20a%20common%20theme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20said%20they%20regretted%20not%20saving%20more%2C%20as%20a%20lack%20of%20money%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-living-social-security-government-aid-snap-loneliness-crisis-isolation-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaintain%20a%20social%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20said%20they%20struggled%20to%20ask%20friends%20and%20family%20for%20help%2C%20further%20isolating%20them%20from%20loved%20ones.%20For%20an%20older%20generation%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-retirement-loneliness-making-friends-lifesaver-solutions-epidemic-happiness-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efacing%20a%20loneliness%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20money%20woes%20are%20making%20it%20worse.%20This%20story%20is%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-savings-social-security-baby-boomers-without-savings-401k-poverty-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20retirement%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ozenne%20is%20trying%20to%20get%20by%20on%20her%20%241%2C739%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emonthly%20Social%20Security%20payments%20and%20the%20money%20she%20cobbles%20together%20through%20part-time%20jobs%20at%20a%20law%20firm%20and%20a%20bowling%20alley.%20She%20said%20her%20schedule%20feels%20nonstop%20but%20she%20needs%20the%20work%20so%20that%20her%20total%20monthly%20income%20is%20slightly%20above%20%243%2C000%2C%20enough%20to%20cover%20her%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOzenne%20said%20that%20her%20budget%20didn't%20allow%20her%20to%20travel%20or%20go%20out%20with%20friends%20and%20that%20she%20felt%20increasingly%20isolated.%20She%20said%20she%20regretted%20not%20saving%20enough%20to%20support%20herself%20in%20her%2060s%20or%2070s%20and%20worries%20she'll%20have%20no%20one%20to%20care%20for%20her%20as%20she%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20mentally%20exhausting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20burden%20to%20anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Are%20you%20an%20older%20American%20with%20any%20life%20regrets%20you'd%20be%20comfortable%20sharing%20with%20a%20reporter%3F%20Please%20fill%20out%20this%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScB-4a6dV6jak2g6t-CoOdxFIENDSZggxHVbvsz6ry4dGoUjg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b0b5e90-d366-4878-bd4d-1d9d641f65e0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELimited%20retirement%20savings%20take%20a%20social%20toll%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20survey%20of%20US%20adults%20commissioned%20by%20Cigna%20and%20conducted%20by%20Morning%20Consult%20in%20late%202021%2C%2063%25%20of%20respondents%20who%20earned%20less%20than%20%2450%2C000%20a%20year%20and%2041%25%20of%20respondents%20over%2066%20said%20they%20felt%20consistently%20lonely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20limited%20income%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecan%20erode%20social%20connections%20for%20older%20adults.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-no-savings-snap-benefits-debt-boomers-experiences-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESocial%20Security%20checks%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20enough%20to%20cover%20many%20retirees'%20bills%2C%20and%20some%20don't%20have%20enough%20of%20a%20nest%20egg%20to%20afford%20a%20night%20out%2C%20holiday%20gifts%2C%20or%20gas%20to%20visit%20family%20members.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20costs%20of%20meals%2C%20flights%2C%20and%20concert%20tickets%20have%20crept%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20'golden%20years'%20are%20not%20golden%20at%20all%3A%20I%20live%20alone%20and%20have%20no%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20respondent%20in%20BI's%20survey%20wrote.%20Another%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20hopeless%2C%20I'm%20lonely%2C%20and%20my%20health%20is%20rapidly%20getting%20worse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Coughlin%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20director%20of%20the%20AgeLab%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-dream-shrinking-smaller-homes-fewer-kids-vacation-time-commutes-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20social%20activities%2C%20housing%2C%20and%20transportation%20could%20lead%20to%20social%20challenges%20for%20retirees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20do%20not%20have%20the%20financial%20resources%2C%20you're%20pretty%20much%20constrained%20where%20you%20live%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20a%20place%20that%20gives%20you%20the%20opportunity%20for%20those%20chance%20collisions%20with%20friends%20and%2C%20frankly%2C%20new%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESusan%20Harper%20lives%20on%20less%20than%20%241%2C000%20in%20monthly%20Social%20Security%2C%20plus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-medicaid-snap-benefits-income-reliance-increases-aging-population-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESNAP%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20she%20has%20no%20nest%20egg%20or%20investments.%20The%2066-year-old%20recently%20moved%20from%20Oregon%20to%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20to%20live%20with%20her%20sister.%20They're%20sharing%20household%20bills%20until%20Harper%20can%20secure%20low-income%20housing%20in%20the%20area.%20(Harper%20is%20on%20a%20waitlist.)%20Harper%20said%20that%20while%20she%20appreciated%20her%20sister%2C%20she%20missed%20her%20community.%20She%20said%20she%20often%20declined%20invitations%20from%20new%20friends%20to%20go%20to%20bars%20or%20restaurants%20because%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarper%20said%20that%20while%20she%20needed%20to%20move%20to%20receive%20financial%20support%20from%20her%20sister%2C%20living%20in%20a%20new%20city%20had%20made%20her%20lonely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20very%20difficult%20time%2C%20and%20it's%20very%20isolating%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEspecially%20as%20I%20get%20older.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b95801b3-43df-4233-93de-f55a91dfa725%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOlder%20adults%20regret%20not%20having%20a%20support%20system%20as%20they%20age%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan's%20National%20Poll%20on%20Healthy%20Aging%20conducted%20in%20March%2C%20older%20adults%20who%20weren't%20working%2C%20who%20lived%20alone%2C%20or%20who%20had%20lower%20household%20incomes%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20report%20feeling%20lonely.%20About%2029%25%20of%20adults%2050%20to%2080%20reported%20feeling%20isolated%20from%20others%20some%20of%20the%20time%20or%20often%20within%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoughlin%20said%20social%20isolation%20could%20exacerbate%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-loneliness-does-to-the-body-and-brain-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk%20of%20cognitive%20and%20physical%20decline%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20older%20adults%2C%20which%20may%20increase%20the%20likelihood%20that%20they%20need%20assisted%20care%20later%20in%20life.%20Genworth%20Financial%2C%20an%20insurance%20company%2C%20found%20that%20the%20median%20monthly%20cost%20of%20an%20assisted%20living%20facility%20in%20the%20US%20was%20%245%2C350%20in%202023%20%E2%80%94%20a%20price%20many%20older%20Americans%20told%20BI%20they%20couldn't%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Keefe%2C%2084%2C%20lives%20alone%20in%20Arkansas%20on%20his%20%242%2C700%20monthly%20Social%20Security%20check%20and%20limited%20retirement%20savings.%20Keefe%20lost%20his%20son%20in%202011%20and%20his%20wife%20in%202023.%20He%20said%20they%20were%20his%20main%20support%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeefe%20said%20he%20didn't%20travel%20much%20outside%20his%20hometown%2C%20and%20he%20worries%20about%20how%20he'll%20take%20care%20of%20himself%20when%20he%20can%20no%20longer%20drive%20to%20appointments%20or%20the%20grocery%20store.%20He%20said%20he%20wished%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20built%20a%20stronger%20financial%20cushion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20outlived%20everybody%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20especially%20challenging%20to%20make%20connections%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwriting-wills-buying-life-insurance-losing-spouses-income-retirement-widows-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewidowed%20retiree%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20there's%20no%20one-size-fits-all%20fix%20for%20loneliness%2C%20Coughlin%20offered%20a%20few%20suggestions.%20He%20said%20prospective%20retirees%20should%20think%20about%20%26quot%3Blongevity%20planning.%26quot%3B%20In%20addition%20to%20building%20a%20nest%20egg%2C%20he%20said%2C%20arranging%20the%20social%20aspects%20of%20retirement%20earlier%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20living%20near%20friends%20and%20family%20and%20developing%20hobbies%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0could%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20loneliness%20later%20and%20help%20people%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20it's%20about%20how%20much%20money%20you've%20saved%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20also%20about%20all%20those%20other%20little%20things%20that%20make%20you%20smile%20and%20contribute%20to%20quality%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20has%20to%20be%20planned%20as%20much%20as%20your%20401(k)%20or%20whether%20you%20had%20your%20annual%20checkup.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGovernment%20and%20local%20assistance%20can%20also%20be%20a%20source%20of%20relief%20for%20older%20Americans%20struggling%20with%20finances%20and%20loneliness.%20The%20National%20Council%20on%20Aging%20estimates%20that%209%20million%20older%20adults%20who%20are%20eligible%20for%20SNAP%20benefits%20don't%20receive%20them%2C%20and%20many%20forgo%20aid%20like%20Medicare%20Savings%20Programs%20designed%20to%20help%20pay%20for%20healthcare%20and%20other%20expenses.%20Many%20local%20senior%20centers%20offer%20free%20or%20low-cost%20social%20activities%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20benefits%20counseling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOzenne%20is%20taking%20her%20life%20day%20by%20day.%20Because%20she%20works%20several%20jobs%2C%20her%20income%20is%20likely%20too%20high%20to%20qualify%20her%20for%20many%20forms%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoverty-line-leaves-behind-low-income-americans-snap-medi