%20Opposition%2C%20which%20seemed%20disorganised%20during%20the%20session%2C%20with%20allies%20distancing%20themselves%20from%20Congress%20slogans%2C%20suddenly%20found%20a%20cause%20to%20rally%20around.%20The%20shameful%20events%20on%20the%20penultimate%20day%20of%20the%20winter%20session%20may%20well%20be%20the%20darkest%20episode%20in%20our%20constitutional%20history.%20MPs%20are%20elected%20to%20debate%20issues%20in%20Parliament%2C%20not%20to%20spar%20like%20gladiators%20at%20its%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Winter%20Session%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20worked%20for%20just%2057%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20while%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20functioned%20for%20only%2043%25.%20Very%20little%20productive%20work%20is%20being%20done%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20focusing%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House%2C%20we%20now%20witness%20hyperactivity%20at%20the%20gates.%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20holds%20mock%20media%20interviews%2C%20and%20Opposition%20MPs%20climb%20the%20ramparts%20of%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building.%20Despite%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker's%20direction%20that%20no%20demonstrations%20be%20held%20at%20the%20gates%2C%20ruling%20party%20MPs%20block%20the%20entrances%20to%20counter%20the%20Opposition%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20fisticuffs%20being%20exchanged%20and%20two%20MPs%20being%20injured%20have%20emerged.%20The%20Delhi%20Police's%20Crime%20Branch%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20Politicians'%20activities%20on%20Parliament%20premises%20are%20now%20subject%20to%20a%20criminal%20probe%E2%80%94an%20unprecedented%20situation%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20parliamentary%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20now%20come%20back%20to%20the%20Ambedkar%20legacy%20and%20who%20has%20claims%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20was%20formed%20in%201946%2C%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20faced%20strong%20opposition%20to%20his%20candidacy%20from%20Congress%20stalwarts%2C%20including%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20failed%20to%20get%20elected%20from%20his%20then%20home%20state%20of%20Bombay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20Bombay%20were%20reportedly%20of%20the%20view%20that%20%E2%80%9Capart%20from%20the%20doors%2C%20the%20windows%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20were%20closed%20to%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar.%E2%80%9D%20The%20reason%20for%20their%20opposition%20stemmed%20from%20Ambedkar's%20differences%20with%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%201933%20fast%20in%20Yerwada%20Jail%20and%20the%20subsequent%20signing%20of%20the%20Poona%20Pact.%20In%201936%2C%20Ambedkar%20had%20also%20formed%20the%20Indian%20Labour%20Party%2C%20which%20contested%20elections%20against%20Congress%20in%20provincial%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Ambedkar%20formed%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20Federation%20(SCF)%2C%20which%20came%20to%20his%20aid%20in%201946%2C%20ensuring%20his%20election%20to%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20from%20the%20Jessore-Khulna%20constituency%20in%20undivided%20Bengal.%20Jogendra%20Nath%20Mandal%2C%20a%20Namosudra%20SCF%20legislator%2C%20helped%20secure%20Ambedkar's%20election%20through%20the%20Bengal%20Legislature.%20Ambedkar%20won%20with%20the%20highest%20votes%2C%20with%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose's%20brother%2C%20Sarat%20Chandra%20Bose%2C%20securing%20one%20vote%20fewer.%20Other%20prominent%20figures%2C%20including%20Shyama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee%20and%20Frank%20Anthony%2C%20were%20also%20elected%20alongside%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20partition%20of%201947%20saw%20Jessore-Khulna%20going%20to%20the%20East%20Bengal%20Province%20of%20the%20Dominion%20of%20Pakistan.%20The%20member%20elected%20from%20Jessore-Khulna%20was%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20Constituent%20Assembly%20in%20Karachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20election%20in%201946%2C%20Ambedkar%20had%20made%20significant%20contributions%20to%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20of%20undivided%20India.%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20thus%20sent%20a%20request%20to%20B.G.%20Kher%2C%20the%20then%20Premier%20(as%20Chief%20Ministers%20were%20called%20at%20the%20time)%20of%20Bombay%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20ensure%20Ambedkar's%20election%20to%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20anxious%20that%20he%20should%20attend%20the%20next%20session%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20commencing%20from%20the%2014th%20of%20July%201947%2C%20and%20it%20is%20therefore%20necessary%20that%20he%20should%20be%20elected%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20wrote%20to%20Kher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKher%20set%20aside%20his%20opposition%2C%20which%20had%20previously%20forced%20Ambedkar%20to%20seek%20election%20from%20Bengal.%20He%20arranged%20for%20the%20member%20from%20Poona%20(Pune)%2C%20Mukund%20Ramrao%20Jayakar%2C%20to%20resign.%20The%20resulting%20by-election%20was%20won%20by%20Ambedkar%2C%20while%20Jayakar%20was%20appointed%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Bombay%20government.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAmbedkar's%20Bengal%20connection%20came%20to%20light%20during%20the%20Winter%20Session%20of%202015%20when%2C%20at%20the%20instance%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Constitution%20Day%20was%20first%20observed%20on%20November%2026.%20Trinamool%20Congress%20floor%20leader%20and%20veteran%20parliamentarian%20Sudip%20Bandopadhyay%20mentioned%20it%20in%20his%20tribute.%20A%20controversy%20followed%2C%20with%20BJP%20MP%20from%20West%20Bengal's%20Darjeeling%20seat%2C%20Surinder%20Ahluwalia%2C%20disputing%20the%20claim%20and%20asserting%20that%20Ambedkar%20was%20elected%20from%20Bombay%20State.%20Both%20MPs%20were%20right.%20%C2%A0Ambedkar%2C%20while%20presiding%20over%20the%20Drafting%20Committee%20(which%20had%2010%20members%2C%20with%20B.N.%20Rau%20writing%20the%20document)%2C%20was%20indeed%20a%20member%20from%20Bombay%20when%20the%20Constitution%20was%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar's%20differences%20with%20Congress%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20resignation%20from%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20cabinet%20in%201951%20and%20his%20subsequent%20unsuccessful%20bids%20to%20enter%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Bombay%20North-Central%20(in%20the%20first%20general%20election%20of%201952)%20and%20from%20Bhandara%20(in%20a%201954%20by-election)%2C%20are%20often%20highlighted.%20It%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%2C%20despite%20contesting%20against%20Congress%20on%20both%20occasions%2C%20he%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%201952%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20Federation%20(SCF).%20This%20was%20made%20possible%20because%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20oppose%20his%20Rajya%20Sabha%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20spotlight%20is%20on%20Ambedkar%2C%20it%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20recall%20the%20comment%20he%20made%20about%20his%20role%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Hindus%20wanted%20the%20Vedas%2C%20and%20they%20sent%20for%20(Ved)%20Vyasa%2C%20who%20was%20not%20a%20caste%20Hindu.%20The%20Hindus%20wanted%20the%20epic%20Ramayana%20and%20they%20sent%20for%20Valmiki%2C%20who%20was%20an%20untouchable.%20The%20Hindus%20want%20a%20constitution%2C%20and%20they%20have%20sent%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20legacy%20of%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20is%20being%20debated%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20recognise%20that%20not%20all%20in%20Congress%20were%20opposed%20to%20him.%20He%20had%20been%20both%20an%20opponent%20and%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20before%20the%20Constitution%20was%20formally%20adopted%20on%20November%2026%2C%201949%2C%20the%20Organiser%2C%20in%20its%20November%2023%2C%201949%20edition%2C%20carried%20an%20article%20by%20the%20then%20RSS%20Sarsanghchalak%20lamenting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cunique%20constitutional%20developments%20in%20ancient%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20had%20been%20glossed%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar's%20Constitution%20of%20India%20is%20a%20product%20of%20competing%20ideas%20that%20were%20incorporated%20into%20a%20historic%20text.%20The%20behaviour%20of%20current%20MPs%2C%20both%20inside%20the%20House%20and%20outside%2C%20stands%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Ambedkarite%20thought%2C%20whose%20legacy%20everyone%20seems%20eager%20to%20usurp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734943500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fbr-ambedkar_650x400_41512541559.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frajendra-prasad-ensured-ambedkars-inclusion-in-constituent-assembly-7313393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20was%20formed%20in%201946%2C%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20faced%20strong%20opposition%20to%20his%20candidacy%20from%20Congress%20stalwarts%2C%20including%20Sardar%20Vallabhbhai%20Patel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frajendra-prasad-ensured-ambedkars-inclusion-in-constituent-assembly-7313393%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BChance%20At%20Centre...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ajit%20Pawar's%201st%20Reaction%20To%20NCP's%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENCP%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fchhagan-bhujbal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChhagan%20Bhujbal%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20sulking%20after%20claiming%20his%20party%20denied%20him%20a%20ministerial%20berth%20in%20the%20new%20Maharashtra%20government%20-%20was%20dealt%20a%20slap%20on%20the%20wrist%20by%20party%20boss%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fajit-pawar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAjit%20Pawar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20public%20reaction%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%20%26quot%3Bsometimes%20new%20people%20have%20to%20be%20given%20a%20chance%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20(without%20naming%20Mr%20Bhujbal)%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20right...%20to%20create%20misunderstandings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20seemed%20to%20hint%20at%20a%20solution%20that%20might%20satisfy%20Mr%20Bhujbal%20-%20who%20was%20among%20the%2040%2B%20MLAs%20to%20side%20with%20him%20in%20the%20rebellion%20last%20year%20against%20NCP%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20we%20have%20also%20thought%20about%20giving%20a%20chance%20to%20older%20people%20at%20the%20centre%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajit%20Pawar%20said%2C%20indicating%20the%2077-year-old%20OBC%20leader%20might%20be%20given%20a%20post%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20are%20expressing%20anger%20because%20they%20were%20not%20taken%20in%20the%20cabinet...%20but%20sometimes%20new%20people%20have%20to%20be%20given%20a%20chance.%20It%20is%20not%20right%20to%20unnecessarily%20create%20misunderstandings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20Monday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20we%20have%20also%20thought%20about%20how%20we%20can%20give%20a%20chance%20to%20(senior)%20people%20at%20the%20centre%20instead%20of%20giving%20them%20another%20chance%20(in%20the%20state%20government).%20Ajit%20Pawar%20will%20never%20disrespect%20others...%20but%20sometimes%20it%20is%20not%20right%20to%20unnecessarily%20create%20misunderstandings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20is%20part%20of%20Mr%20Modi's%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20state%20(as%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20alliance)%20and%20federal%20(as%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance)%20levels.%20In%20return%20for%20the%20support%20of%20its%2041%20MLAs%2C%20the%20party%20has%20been%20given%2C%20so%20far%2C%20nine%20ministerial%20berths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-takes-oath-as-maharashtra-chief-minister-for-3rd-time-7179169%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ED%20Fadnavis%20New%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20E%20Shinde%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Deputies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20none%20of%20those%20berths%20fell%20to%20Mr%20Bhujbal%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20the%20state's%20Food%2C%20Civil%20Supplies%2C%20and%20Consumer%20Protection%20Minister.%20Mr%20Bhujbal%20-%20who%20has%20sway%20among%20the%20state's%20OBC%20voters%20-%20responded%20with%20a%20fierce%20swipe%20at%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20another%20senior%20NCP%20leader%2C%20Praful%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAjit%20Pawar%20and%20Praful%20Patel%20had%20said%20they%20will%20talk%20to%20me%20about%20a%20ministerial%20berth.%20But%20they%20did%20not...%20no%20one%20from%20Ajit%20Pawar%20or%20Praful%20Patel's%20office%20called%20me.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20toy%20in%20their%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20Nashik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhujbal%20is%20the%20MLA%20from%20Yevla%20in%20Nashik%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-your-toy-chhagan-bhujbal-to-ajit-pawar-on-exclusion-from-cabinet-7271263%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNot%20Your%20Toy%26quot%3B%3A%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%20To%20Ajit%20Pawar%20On%20Cabinet%20Snub%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhujbal%20has%20claimed%20that%20his%20appointment%20to%20the%20state%20cabinet%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20been%20cleared%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20but%20that%20his%20NCP%20colleagues%20held%20back%20on%20his%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFadnavis%20wanted%20me...%20(state%20BJP%20chief%20Chandrashekhar)%20Bawankule%20told%20me%20that%20till%20the%20end%20Fadnavis%20was%20trying%20to%20push%20for%20me.