y.%20The%20joyous%20couple%20shared%20the%20news%20via%20a%20heartwarming%20social%20media%20video%2C%20showcasing%20tender%20moments%20with%20their%20newborn.%20The%20video%20features%20the%20couple%20holding%20their%20baby's%20tiny%20feet%20and%20hands%2C%20concluding%20with%20a%20shot%20of%20teddy%20bears%20and%20a%20baby%20doll.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmusician-couple-sachet-and-parampara-blessed-with-a-baby-boy%2Farticleshow%2F116590556.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Steering%2C%20Throttle%20Fault%20May%20Be%20Behind%20Ferry%20Crash%2C%20Navy%20Crew%20Knew%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20collision%20between%20a%20Navy%20boat%20and%20a%20passenger%20ferry%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Mumbai%20on%20December%2018%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%2015%20deaths%2C%20was%20likely%20caused%20by%20a%20technical%20malfunction%20in%20the%20steering%20assembly%20and%20in%20the%20throttle%20quadrant%20which%20governs%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20boat%2C%20Navy%20sources%20have%20said.%20The%20boat%20was%20travelling%20at%20a%20high%20speed%20when%20it%20made%20an%20impact%20with%20the%20tourist%20ferry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20survivor%20on%20board%20the%20Navy%20vessel%2C%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20manufacturer%20of%20the%20boat%20which%20was%20being%20tested%20before%20induction%2C%20has%20indicated%20that%20the%20crew%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20malfunction%20when%20the%20collision%20took%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20of%20the%20incident%20show%20an%20effort%20being%20made%20to%20steer%20the%20craft%20away%20from%20the%20ferry%20but%20the%20Navy%20boat%20was%20unable%20to%20turn%20away%20sharply%20enough%20to%20avoid%20the%20accident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20craft%2C%20a%20Rigid%20Hull%20Inflatable%20Boat%20(RHIB)%2C%20was%20undergoing%20engine%20trials%20at%20high%20speed%2C%20lost%20control%20and%20collided%20with%20the%20passenger%20ferry%20Neel%20Kamal.%20The%20ferry%2C%20carrying%20more%20than%20100%20passengers%2C%20was%20en%20route%20from%20the%20Gateway%20of%20India%20to%20Elephanta%20Island%2C%20a%20popular%20tourist%20destination%20known%20for%20its%20ancient%20cave%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collision%20caused%20the%20ferry%20to%20sink%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20maritime%20accidents%20in%20the%20city's%20harbour.%20Naval%20helicopters%20and%20boats%2C%20along%20with%20Coast%20Guard%20vessels%2C%20were%20deployed%20in%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations%20following%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20113%20individuals%20aboard%20the%20two%20vessels%2C%2015%20died%2C%20while%2098%20others%20were%20rescued%2C%20including%20two%20who%20were%20injured.%20On%20the%20Navy%20craft%2C%20which%20had%20six%20crew%20members%2C%20only%20two%20survived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20records%20from%20the%20Maharashtra%20Maritime%20Board%20(MMB)%2C%20the%20Neel%20Kamal%20was%20licensed%20to%20carry%20a%20maximum%20of%2084%20passengers%20and%20six%20crew%20members.%20However%2C%20the%20ferry%20was%20overloaded%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20collision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MMB%20has%20since%20cancelled%20the%20ferry's%20licence%20and%20launched%20its%20own%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter.%20A%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20Navy%20craft's%20driver%20at%20the%20Colaba%20police%20station%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%2C%20including%20charges%20related%20to%20negligence%2C%20endangering%20public%20safety%20and%20rash%20navigation.%20The%20Navy%20craft%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20naval%20authorities%2C%20though%20police%20have%20indicated%20they%20will%20request%20access%20to%20the%20vessel%20as%20needed%20for%20their%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734936120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fbkb2s6s8_mumbai-boat-accident_625x300_19_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-ferry-crash-steering-fault-caused-mumbai-ferry-crash-navy-crew-was-aware-sources-7312550%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20collision%20between%20a%20Navy%20boat%20and%20a%20passenger%20ferry%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Mumbai%20on%20December%2018%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%2015%20deaths%2C%20was%20likely%20caused%20by%20a%20technical%20malfunction%20in%20the%20steering%20assembly%20and%20in%20the%20throttle%20quadrant%2C%20Navy%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-ferry-crash-steering-fault-caused-mumbai-ferry-crash-navy-crew-was-aware-sources-7312550%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCongress%20Should%20Be%20Ready...%26quot%3B%3A%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar's%20Big%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20should%20be%20ready%20to%20not%20be%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20veteran%20party%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20has%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fmani-shankar-aiyar-congress-india-bloc-leader-rahul-gandhi-9739696%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0Asked%20if%20any%20other%20party%20could%20lead%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20Mr%20Aiyar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20it's%20a%20relevant%20question.%20I%20think%20the%20Congress%20should%20be%20ready%20to%20not%20be%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20bloc.%20Let%20whoever%20wants%20to%20be%20the%20leader%20be%20the%20leader.%20There%20is%20competence%20in%20Mamata%20Banerjee...%20There%20is%20competence%20in%20others%20in%20the%20alliance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20don't%20care%20who%20becomes%20the%20leader%20because%20I%20think%20the%20position%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20of%20the%20Congress%20leader%20will%20always%20be%20a%20major%20one.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20the%20only%20one.%20It%20will%20be%20the%20major%20one%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20I%20am%20sure%20Rahul%20(Gandhi)%20will%20be%20treated%20with%20even%20more%20respect%20than%20he%20would%20be%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2083-year-old%2C%20who%20has%20come%20out%20with%20the%20second%20volume%20of%20his%20autobiography%20A%20Maverick%20in%20Politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20Congress%20leader's%20remarks%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20leadership%20tussle%20within%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20formed%20last%20year%20to%20take%20on%20the%20BJP's%20formidable%20election%20machinery.%20The%20grand%20alliance%20strategy%20worked%20well%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20was%20restricted%20to%20below%20the%20majority%20mark.%20The%20alliance%2C%20however%2C%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20tricky%20in%20regions%20where%20two%20INDIA%20partners%20are%20electoral%20rivals.%20This%20has%20drawn%20attacks%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20termed%20the%20bloc%20%26quot%3Bopportunistic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20doubled%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20score%20this%20time%2C%20has%20since%20suffered%20setbacks%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20polls.%20Soon%20after%20the%20Maharashtra%20results%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20and%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20took%20a%20veiled%20swipe%20at%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party.%20She%20said%20%26quot%3Beveryone%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20along%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20moves%20against%20the%20BJP-ruled%20central%20government.%20Asked%20why%20she%20was%20not%20taking%20charge%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20given%20the%20opportunity%2C%20I%20would%20ensure%20its%20smooth%20functioning.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20outside%20Bengal%2C%20but%20I%20can%20run%20it%20from%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20Opposition%20leaders%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20threw%20their%20weight%20behind%20Ms%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress's%20objection%20means%20nothing.%20We%20will%20support%20Mamata...%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20should%20be%20given%20the%20leadership%20(of%20the%20INDIA%20Bloc)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RJD%20founder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCP%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20certainly%20(she%20is%20capable%20of%20leading%20the%20alliance).%20She%20is%20a%20prominent%20leader%20of%20this%20nation...%20she%20has%20that%20capability.%20The%20elected%20leaders%20she%20sent%20to%20Parliament%20are%20responsible%2C%20dutiful%2C%20and%20well-aware%20people.%20Therefore%2C%20she%20has%20the%20right%20to%20say%20so.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20had%20said%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20should%20be%20a%20major%20partner%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20this%20opinion%20of%20Mamata%20ji.%20We%20also%20want%20her%20to%20be%20a%20major%20partner%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20Whether%20it%20is%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20or%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20we%20are%20all%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734936060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F6bb6frio_mani-shankar-aiyar_625x300_15_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-should-be-ready-mani-shankar-aiyars-big-india-bloc-remark-7312593%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20should%20be%20ready%20to%20not%20be%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20veteran%20party%20leader%20an