.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fousted-syrian-president-assads-wife-files-for-divorce-unhappy-in-moscow-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F116588308.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fousted-syrian-president-assads-wife-files-for-divorce-unhappy-in-moscow-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F116588308.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manu%20Bhaker%20Surprise%20Absentee%20From%20Khel%20Ratna%20Nominations%2C%20Reason%20Is...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202024%20has%20been%20a%20memorable%20year%20for%20Indian%20sports%20as%20many%20athletes%20showed%20their%20true%20caliber%20and%20brought%20accolades%20for%20the%20country.%20From%20India's%20magnificent%20win%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20to%20Manu%20Bhaker's%20historic%20double%20medal%20victory%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20Indian%20sports%20reached%20new%20heights.%20Just%20like%20every%20year%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20will%20be%20giving%20the%20prestigious%20Major%20Dhyan%20Chand%20Khel%20Ratna%20Award%20to%20celebrate%20and%20honour%20the%20achievements%20of%20these%20athletes%20and%20some%20nominees%20of%20the%20same%20have%20been%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20men's%20hockey%20team%20captain%20and%20ace%20drag-flicker%20Harmanpreet%20Singh%20has%20been%20recommended%20for%20India's%20highest%20sporting%20honour.%20Under%20Harmanpreet's%20captaincy%2C%20India%20clinched%20the%20bronze%20medal%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20in%20men's%20hockey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPara-athlete%20Praveen%20Kumar%20has%20also%20been%20nominated%20for%20the%20Khel%20Ratna%20award.%20Praveen%20won%20gold%20in%20the%20men's%20high%20jump%20T64%20class%20with%20an%20Asian%20record%20at%20the%20Paris%20Paralympics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20shocking%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20India's%20shooter%20and%20double-medal%20winner%20Manu%20Bhaker's%20name%20is%20not%20in%20the%20list%20of%20the%C2%A0recommendations%20for%20the%20Khel%20Ratna.%C2%A0%