tion%20of%20who%20I%20am.%20It%20gives%20me%20a%20sense%20of%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaspreet%20Kaur%2C%20a%20younger%20resident%20of%20the%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20to%20see%20the%20change%20in%20the%20mindset%20of%20the%20younger%20generation.%20They%20see%20women%20leading%2C%20and%20they%20aspire%20to%20be%20like%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paramjit%20Singh%20Bhullar%2C%20who%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20bringing%20to%20life%20the%20initiative%2C%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20small%20step%2C%20but%20it%20made%20a%20huge%20difference.%20For%20generations%2C%20our%20society%20had%20only%20recognised%20men.%20Sheshandeep%E2%80%99s%20vision%20was%20fresh%2C%20and%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291700%2Fruma-devi-barmer-invited-by-harvard-for-empowering-women-via-fashion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egave%20women%20the%20recognition%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20had%20always%20deserved.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20phase%2C%20a%20shared%20vision%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20her%20term%20as%20%3Cem%3ESarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20ended%20in%20March%202024%2C%20Sheshandeep%20continued%20to%20work%20towards%20the%20betterment%20of%20women%20in%20her%20village.%20She%20is%20now%20leading%20a%20project%20with%20%E2%80%98Read%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20initiative%20that%20teaches%20skills%20like%20stitching%20and%20computer%20literacy%20to%20marginalised%20women%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20women%20who%20wish%20to%20work%20can%20do%20so%2C%20and%20they%20can%20earn%20independently.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20me%20that%20women%20have%20the%20skills%20they%20need%20to%20succeed%20in%20the%20workforce%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20s