%20sapling%20of%20another%20(called%20the%20scion).%20He%20sources%20the%20rootstock%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20uses%20scions%20from%20his%20existing%20plants.%20This%20technique%20not%20only%20improves%20the%20health%20of%20the%20plants%20but%20also%20enhances%20their%20yield%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrafting%20costs%20around%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20Parmeshwar%20grafted%20around%20250%20new%20saplings.%20These%20plants%20are%20expected%20to%20start%20fruiting%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20%E2%80%9CGrafting%20is%20a%20game-changer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20extends%20the%20lifespan%20of%20avocado%20plants%20and%20boosts%20their%20yield%20potential.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%2C%20a%2062-year-old%20retired%20postal%20employee%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20supporting%20Parmeshwar%20by%20supplying%20avocado%20plants%20for%20his%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20I%20come%20from%20a%20non-farming%20background%2C%20we%20both%20began%20this%20journey%20of%20avocado%20farming%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Parmeshwar%20visited%20Karnataka%20to%20learn%20about%20avocado%20cultivation%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20Kannada%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20met.%20I%20explained%20everything%20to%20him.%20His%20perseverance%20and%20dedication%20were%20clear%2C%20and%20over%20time%2C%20they%20helped%20him%20become%20a%20successful%20avocado%20farmer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20avocado%20saplings%20I%20planted%20have%20yet%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20thriving%2C%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20now%20successfully%20harvesting%20avocados!%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20by%20example%3A%20Educating%20the%20next%20generation%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20avocado%20farming%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-agriculture-solar-dryer-biofertiliser-tree-scooter-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremarkable%20story%20of%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20sustainable%20practices.%20What%20started%20with%20just%2050%20saplings%20on%20a%20small%20plot%20of%20land%20has%20now%20blossomed%20into%20a%20thriving%201.75-acre%20farm%20%E2%80%94%20home%20to%20300%20avocado%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20harvested%20and%20sold%20around%201%2C200%20kg%20of%20avocados%2C%20earning%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%205-6%20lakh%20after%20selling%20each%20fruit%20at%20Rs%20200.%E2%80%9D%20He%20mentions%20that%20maintaining%20the%20farm%20costs%20him%20about%20Rs%2050%2C000%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20selling%20the%20fruit%2C%20he%20has%20also%20ventured%20into%20selling%20avocado%20saplings.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20sold%202%2C300%20saplings%20at%20Rs%20300%20each.%20After%20accounting%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20have%20made%20a%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%204.6%20lakh%20from%20sapling%20sales.%20In%20total%2C%20his%20net%20profit%20for%20the%20year%202023%20was%20approximately%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201971px)%20100vw%2C%201971px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-03-at-19.40.30-1_11zon-1734346437.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221971%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22He%20sells%20his%20avocados%20via%20local%20markets%20in%20Beed%20and%20Pune%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-03-at-19.40.30-1_11zon-1734346437.jpeg%201971w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.t